<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men tuán jù zài zhè lǐ 迦南36</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ shǐ wǒ men tuán jù zài zhè lǐ, zhǔ shǐ wǒ men zhè yàng xiāng shì,
 hé mù tóng jū hé děng de měi shàn! rén shì jiān nán yǐ zhǎo xún, kě shì
 wǒ men hái yào fēn shǒu, bēn nà bǎi zài qián miàn de lù. qǐng nǐ zhēn xī zhè
 fèn guāng yīn, ràng zhǔ de líng dài lǐng wǒ men, jiān fù wěi dà guāng róng de shǐ mìng.
 wǒ men dōu shì tiān guó de shǐ chén. fàng yǎn tiān xià nǐ wǒ zǒu yī tàng, yào jiāng zhēn
 lǐ yáng qǐ lái. zhǔ de líng zài wǒ men de shēn shàng, jiāng zhǔ de huà yǔ chuán dào liè
 bāng, bào gào shén yuè nà de xǐ nián, shòu yā dé zì yóu bèi lǔ dé shì fàng,
 mài kāi dà bù xiàng qián zǒu zhōng xīn wèi zhǔ bù xū dù shí guāng. wǒ men hái yǒu xiāng féng
 de shí kè, nà shì zài chuán fú yīn de dà dào shàng, nà shì zài chuán fú
 yīn de dà dào shàng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>36</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>